852
01:11:50,976 --> 01:11:52,144
Yes.

853
01:11:53,313 --> 01:11:54,980
He runs a newspaper downstate.

854
01:11:56,358 --> 01:11:58,818
He's the editor, yes.

855
01:12:03,489 --> 01:12:05,740
