a dear friend.

900
01:18:25,204 --> 01:18:28,873
You served me and this country
brilliantly.

901
01:18:28,875 --> 01:18:31,416
A service
that I believe deserves

902
01:18:31,418 --> 01:18:34,003
to be recognized and honored.

903
01:18:34,005 --> 01:18:35,838
I was at a party recently

904
