906
01:18:40,761 --> 01:18:41,970
Of course I do.

907
01:18:43,972 --> 01:18:45,225
A hundred and fifty.

908
01:18:46,725 --> 01:18:48,934
One hundred and fifty thousand
people

909
01:18:48,936 --> 01:18:50,229
