You wanted out.

983
01:24:21,310 --> 01:24:24,269
I agreed to everything.

984
01:24:24,271 --> 01:24:26,147
Everything!

985
01:24:26,149 --> 01:24:29,736
But for you to go
and write this betrayal?

986
01:24:32,072 --> 01:24:37,075
'Cause that's exactly what
it is. It is a betrayal.

987
01:24:37,077 --> 01:24:38,369
A betrayal for you.

988
01:24:40,287 --> 01:24:41,622
A reckoning for me.

989
01:24:49,421 --> 01:24:50,629
Madam President, you are needed.

990
01:24:50,631 --> 01:24:51,715
