I mean, I owe her that much.

993
01:25:21,121 --> 01:25:24,205
Alright.
So, tell me about Salhi.

994
01:25:24,207 --> 01:25:26,292
Well, they lost him
in Union Station.

995
01:25:28,627 --> 01:25:30,460
Thirty seconds of confusion
is about all it took.

996
01:25:30,462 --> 01:25:33,296
- How is that even possible?
- He's a smart kid.

997
01:25:33,298 --> 01:25:36,718
He found the tracker and stashed
it along with his laptop

998
01:25:36,720 --> 01:25:39,178
in a bag on a bus
headed to Des Moines.

999
01:25:39,180 --> 01:25:41,304
I know we thought the boy
would lead us to other copies

1000
01:25:41,306 --> 01:25:43,143
but leaving the backpack
was a mistake.

1001
01:25:44,476 --> 01:25:47,812
We did go back and check
the security videos.

1002
01:25:47,814 --> 01:25:51,273
Salhi purchased a bus ticket
to Springfield

1003
01:25:51,275 --> 01:25:52,943
and we have him boarding
that bus.

1004
01:25:54,612 --> 01:25:56,111
- Pull your team.
- That would be a mistake.

1005
01:25:56,113 --> 01:25:57,487
The operation is blown.

1006
01:25:57,489 --> 01:25:59,240
The pads are in a backpack,
which can be easily

1007
01:25:59,242 --> 01:26:00,282
