1008
01:26:00,284 --> 01:26:01,742
It'll look like
a simple mugging.

1009
01:26:01,744 --> 01:26:03,619
No. It's already light
in the Midwest.

1010
01:26:03,621 --> 01:26:05,287
No. It's too risky. No.

1011
01:26:05,289 --> 01:26:07,080
Madam President,
there are people that don't

1012
