1023
01:26:39,990 --> 01:26:43,036
Commission-proof intel
is the phrase I remember.

1024
01:26:45,872 --> 01:26:48,291
- This is dangerous.
- Oh, we'll weather it. Stop it.

1025
01:26:51,543 --> 01:26:53,046
What should we do with the boy?

1026
01:26:54,338 --> 01:26:57,050
Let him go.
I mean, he's the messenger.

1027
01:26:58,885 --> 01:27:00,302
And Libby?

1028
01:27:03,055 --> 01:27:04,473
Take her home.

1029
01:27:06,350 --> 01:27:08,603
It'll be her word against ours.

1030
01:27:19,072 --> 01:27:21,321
