1037
01:29:14,854 --> 01:29:18,606
Yes.

1038
01:29:50,097 --> 01:29:52,809
I'm... I'm Martin Salhi.
I'm here to see Phillip Lamm.

1039
01:29:55,895 --> 01:29:57,562
You can say it's regarding
his daughter, Elizabeth.

1040
01:29:57,564 --> 01:29:58,898
Let me try him.

